#: ../../doc/compare.rst:2
msgid "Comparing Script Objects"
msgstr "比较脚本对象"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:4
msgid ""
"When implementing a container for script objects, you need a way to compare "
"elements — for ``operator==``, ``operator<=>``, ``std::sort``, or "
"deduplication. AngelScript classes can define ``opEquals`` and ``opCmp`` "
"methods, but calling them from C++ requires discovering them at runtime."
msgstr ""
"当实现脚本对象的容器时，您需要一种比较元素的方法——用于 ``operator==``、"
"``operator<=>``、``std::sort`` 或去重。AngelScript 类可以定义 ``opEquals`` 和 "
"``opCmp`` 方法，但从 C++ 调用它们需要在运行时发现这些方法。"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:9
msgid ""
"``container/compare.hpp`` provides tools to inspect a script type for these "
"methods and invoke them through a uniform interface."
msgstr ""
"``container/compare.hpp`` 提供了检查脚本类型是否有这些方法并通过统一接口调用它"
"们的工具。"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:13
msgid ""
"The content of this file is designed for library developers implementing "
"containers. If you are not building a custom container for script objects, "
"you likely do not need these APIs."
msgstr ""
"本文档内容面向实现容器的库开发者。如果您不是在构建自定义的脚本对象容器，您大概"
"不需要这些 API。"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:18
msgid "Discovering Comparators"
msgstr "发现比较器"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:20
msgid ""
"Call ``get_comparator`` with an ``asITypeInfo*`` to scan the type's methods. "
"It looks for methods matching these signatures:"
msgstr ""
"使用 ``asITypeInfo*`` 调用 ``get_comparator`` 来扫描类型的方法。它会寻找匹配以"
"下签名的方法："

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:23
msgid "``bool opEquals(const T&in) const``"
msgstr "``bool opEquals(const T&in) const``"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:24
msgid "``int opCmp(const T&in) const``"
msgstr "``int opCmp(const T&in) const``"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:48
msgid "Using the Comparator"
msgstr "使用比较器"

#: ../../doc/compare.rst:50
msgid ""
"Once obtained, ``script_element_comparator`` provides ``eq()`` and "
"``compare()`` that invoke the discovered script methods. Both take a script "
"context and two ``const void*`` pointers to the elements."
msgstr ""
"一旦获取到，``script_element_comparator`` 提供 ``eq()`` 和 ``compare()`` 来调用"
"发现的脚本方法。两者都需要一个脚本上下文和两个指向元素的 ``const void*`` 指针。"

